<sec id="id-daf6e4e2-38bf-4487-c16b-7f46c517f894"><title><bold><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="a7d15065-7b33-4349-d7e2-9b8befa78fc5" timestamp="1666104837288"?>Organization Salary Record<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="a7d15065-7b33-4349-d7e2-9b8befa78fc5"?></bold></title><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="5191008" change-id="cf35a31b-b113-4a0f-ad50-fc6ba04e0457" text="Organization Salary Record" timestamp="1666104835660"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="6410c5b2-b12b-40d7-e450-6b00effafa9f" text="[Former box 5]" timestamp="1675426732143"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="fd2bc7da-1d61-45d0-cffd-ce70d4d5d399" timestamp="1666104845704"?><p>All companies, regardless of their size, should record company remuneration of all employees, to guarantee the obligation of <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="fd2bc7da-1d61-45d0-cffd-ce70d4d5d399"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="9338e56d-f3b3-4ad9-c39d-7d7612a548cf" text="E" timestamp="1670263794964"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="f058d63f-8c0d-4a8a-c89f-133924000eff" timestamp="1670263795771"?>e<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="f058d63f-8c0d-4a8a-c89f-133924000eff"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="8eae1189-b95a-40bd-bb38-5be66252593a" timestamp="1666104845704"?>qual retribution for work of equal value.</p><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="8eae1189-b95a-40bd-bb38-5be66252593a"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="f6c272f7-7ec8-48df-bfcb-ff44aed4230a" text=" work" timestamp="1668679628613"?><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="a7a12a0b-1534-4f5e-feda-765c3284a1bb" timestamp="1666104822569"?>Salary Record should include:<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="a7a12a0b-1534-4f5e-feda-765c3284a1bb"?></p><list list-type="dash"><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="c3ce3283-c26a-47af-c8f4-cf480a4ef36f" timestamp="1666104822569"?><list-item id="id-07599680-0dc1-4752-d655-10303bda5717"><p>All employees, including <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="c3ce3283-c26a-47af-c8f4-cf480a4ef36f"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="f5c155a2-ce6d-4538-e057-a2083ada0087" timestamp="1670263996686"?>top management and governing bodies<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="f5c155a2-ce6d-4538-e057-a2083ada0087"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="4b27b8da-c913-4dc8-fb14-93002aef9710" text="managers and council responsibility roles" timestamp="1670263991853"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="ad010178-3db3-4125-d38e-051cba6f3410" timestamp="1666104822569"?>.</p></list-item><list-item id="id-f82d3f79-0dad-4efb-911e-b854d012c38b"><p>Gender-disaggregated data for average and median values of base salary and <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="ad010178-3db3-4125-d38e-051cba6f3410"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="3d1d6cb8-a8d9-4cdf-f2aa-29fc1575deaa" text="each one of s" timestamp="1670263832980"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="cd4ae52b-ff9b-419c-ff8e-365546fec368" timestamp="1670263846947"?>other compensation and benefit components <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="cd4ae52b-ff9b-419c-ff8e-365546fec368"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="f6d0dda8-9cad-41ce-d52a-8c7e47885615" text="alary supplements and non-salary perceptions " timestamp="1670264062128"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="90d4ceb5-41df-421c-97b5-8f85f5e52a77" timestamp="1666104822569"?>in each professional group, category or level in the company.</p></list-item><list-item id="id-c86bb5bf-14b7-4a51-e776-debc7f8bf5ee"><p>The reference time period will generally be the calendar year</p></list-item><list-item id="id-69c40e46-a64f-4c5b-e007-8366c8edfd18"><p>It should be accessible for employees’ representatives, governmental authorities and for remuneration audits that check the obligation for equal pay.</p></list-item><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="90d4ceb5-41df-421c-97b5-8f85f5e52a77"?></list><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="d6e33807-eff0-46eb-92a0-d0a80e11e177" timestamp="1666104822569"?>Moreover, all companies with at least 50 employees, should be required to carry out a salary audit, including a job evaluation to <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="d6e33807-eff0-46eb-92a0-d0a80e11e177"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="831da8f5-e9c6-4c2c-8169-6f90d3fbb14c" text="assure equal pay for " timestamp="1670264156154"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="83cb9982-33c1-4c74-8287-66120ddfe6c2" timestamp="1670264156153"?>secure equal pay for equal work<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="83cb9982-33c1-4c74-8287-66120ddfe6c2"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="d92d222a-b185-4b94-bc7b-f875b1e2dbc1" text="work of equal value" timestamp="1670264156154"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="b2b2eb73-fea9-4a38-8bac-8dcb84e2e63a" text=" work" timestamp="1668679639504"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="fb771e9b-9cdc-43a3-87b0-dfd2268ae79e" timestamp="1666104822569"?> and justify any wage gap higher than the legally stablished, if it applies.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="fb771e9b-9cdc-43a3-87b0-dfd2268ae79e"?></p><p/></sec>